title: Ep. 452 - Our Leaders Are Gasbags
description:
Democratic congressman Eric Swalwell broadcast hot air on MSNBC last night, but not so much as Democratic senator Chris Murphy or House Speaker Nancy Pelosi. We will examine shameless gasbaggery. Then, across the pond, the UK’s Prince Andrew sweats over questions about his relationship with Jeffrey Epstein, who didn’t kill himself, a New Zealand hunter gets death threats to killing her own food, and conservatives’ favorite chicken restaurant gives in to the leftist mob. Date: 11-19-2019
